dct_title_s: Cranbury Township and Middlesex County text after 1875
dct_description_sm: Plate 19 of a multi page publication. Text describes the boroughs and townships in Middlesex County including Bonhamtown, Metuchen, Stelton, and Cranbury Township. A map of the latter area is part of the same publication. Text indicates history of area up to and including 1875. Latter part of text consists of profiles of local businesses and industries.
